snippet.title: Laadla (1994) Full Hindi Movie (4K) Sridevi & Anil Kapoor & Raveena | Farida Jalal | Bollywood Movie
snippet.description:
Laadla is a 1994 Indian Bollywood action drama film, directed by Raj Kanwar and produced by Nitin Manmohan. The film stars Anil Kapoor, Sridevi, and Raveena Tandon in pivotal roles. And Farida Jalal, Aruna Irani, Anupam Kher, Prem Chopra, Paresh Rawal, Mohnish Behl, Shakti Kapoor, Alok Nath, Arun Bakshi others in supportive role. It is known for its strong dialogues, emotional story and powerful performances.

The story revolves around Raju (Anil Kapoor), a hardworking and principled man who is hired by a ruthless and arrogant factory owner, Sheetal (Sridevi). Their personalities clash due to their different ideologies. Raju believes in honesty and humanity, while Sheetal believes in power and control. Their constant conflict leads to unexpected developments, including a dramatic marriage twist that changes their lives. 

लाडला (1994) एक भारतीय बॉलीवुड एक्शन-ड्रामा फिल्म है, जिसका निर्देशन राज कंवर ने किया है और निर्माण नितिन मनमोहन ने किया है। इस फिल्म में अनिल कपूर, श्रीदेवी और रवीना टंडन लीड रोल में हैं, तो वहीं फरीदा जलाल, अरुणा ईरानी, अनुपम खेर, प्रेम चोपड़ा, परेश रावल,मोहनीश बहल, शक्ति कपूर, आलोक नाथ और अरुण बख्शी सपोर्टिंव रोल में नजर आते हैं। 

कहानी एक ईमानदार और मेहनती आदमी राजू (अनिल कपूर) की है, जिसे एक घमंडी और सख्त फैक्ट्री मालकिन शीतल (श्रीदेवी) द्वारा काम पर रखा जाता है। राजू और शीतल की सोच में ज़मीन-आसमान का फर्क है। एक इंसानियत में विश्वास करता है, तो दूसरी ताकत और नियंत्रण में। उनके बीच का टकराव एक ऐसे मोड़ पर पहुंचता है, जहां एक अप्रत्याशित शादी उनके जीवन को बदल कर रख देती है।

Movie:– Laadla (1994)
Director :-  Raj Kanwar
Produre :- Nitin Manmohan
Cast:- Anil Kapoor, Sridevi, Raveena Tandon, Farida Jalal, Aruna Irani, Anupam Kher, Prem Chopra, Paresh Rawal, Mohnish Behl, Shakti Kapoor, Alok Nath, Arun Bakshi 
Music:- Anand–Milind
Genre:- Action Drama
Language: Hindi

snippet.title: Romeo S3 - Full Movie | Palak Tiwari, Thakur Anoop Singh | Pen Movies | New Hindi Movie 2025
snippet.description:
Romeo S3, directed by Guddu Dhanoa and produced by Pen Studios and Wild River Pictures, is an adrenaline-fueled Hindi action thriller set in the underworld of Goa.
Thakur Anoop Singh stars as DCP Sangram Singh Shekhawat, a fearless cop who goes undercover to dismantle a dangerous drug cartel while uncovering a sinister virus-linked conspiracy.
Opposing him is Palak Tiwari’s investigative journalist, Tanu, whose dogged pursuit of truth pulls her into Sangram’s high-stakes mission.
Packed with explosive fight scenes, high-speed chases, and larger-than-life stunts, the film delivers classic masala action in a bold, cinematic.
While praised for its sheer energy and punchy performances, critics note the storyline sometimes leans on predictable tropes and formulaic twists.

snippet.title: Aarush Laila in ROAST MODE For 2 Hours |  @sadhikasehgal  | Aarush Laila Podcast | @aarushbhola17
snippet.description:
Aarush & Laila are BACK—and this time, it’s personal, hilarious, and completely unfiltered. From Delhi boys’ raw banter to deep friendship talks, this episode with host Sadhika Sehgal is packed with madness, emotion, and chaos.

They kick off by revisiting the prank they pulled on Manmansh Judeja, and quickly spiral into everything from acting gay, talking about virginity, to emotional revelations like Aarush buying his first house and the bond he shares with his dad, who Laila calls “the friend we never had.”

Expect savage birthday pranks (yes, the fake bike gift happened), awkward confessions (who Laila would date if he were gay), and brutal honesty about relationships - including why Aarush hates Laila’s girlfriend and thinks he deserves better. Aarush even exposes how Laila shares his live location with her 24/7, calling it toxic love at its peak.

You’ll hear wild stories of Laila almost getting arrested, calling his married ex while drunk, and getting slapped more than once, while Aarush remains surprisingly untouched by trouble. From gym talk to their very different music tastes, approaching girls at the gym, and even their gym playlists—nothing is off-limits. We also get a peek into their spiritual sides, with stories about Vrindavan trips, Lord Krishna, and Hanuman bhakti.

They spill tea on fake influencers, industry rivalry, and their Samay Raina’s India’s Got Latent Show experience.

They end with future dreams—Netflix series auditions, acting goals, their love languages, and the most chaotic Manali trip ever—think fire extinguishers, scared friends, and hotel staff complaints.

From friendship after 30, trusting each other with their girlfriends, to Delhi food recommendations and relationship red flags, this episode is a full ride - messy, meaningful, and made for everyone who’s ever had a best friend they can fight and laugh with at the same time.

Lyrics :
Ni baitha mai trakki de mathe ch jhanda gaddke
Ni utte nahio aaya thalle kise de vi laggke
Oh hun mera changa aaya kehnde pair chhad gya
Ni jehde maade time ch gye si hath chhadke
Oh lanka nahio dhayi bhave bheti aa harek de
Ni mere saale kinne hi jo bahre pye aa hate de
Ni bahoteya de rang udd janda kude face to
Ni charno da dohta baitha gaddi vich vekhke
Ho vekhi mardanya eh rang kartar de
Oh aap mar jande jehde doojeya nu maarde
Ho bahn jihdi fadi hove neeli Chhatt wale ne
Ni kitho sutt hona a laler nehri taarke
Oh chhetti hath aunde nahio uchiya udariyaan
Ni reejh na pugaiye asi vair nale yaariyan
Oh vairi voori vekhke badak maar dyidi
Ni kudi jandi vekh kde whistlaan ni maariyan
Ni gabhru rakaane bebe bapu ji to baahre na
Na saade kolo vaade hone lagne ve laare na
Ni tere kolo main vi tere maa-pe charwaune na
Te mere kolo ranjhe wangu pashu jaane chaare na
Na dil to greeb bhave bhute na ameer ni
Aa jehde nal bhai kathi kri na mandeer ni
Ni susti na nede tede mitran de laggdi 
Ni 24 ghante lor vich rehnda ae sareer ni
Ni bhaiyan te yakeen security jeyo z te
Ho bade dil lutte akh mittraa di red ne
Ho dabb nal lgga jo rakaane 30 bore da
Flower bna dewe bhaida eh forehead te
Na nimm jehe lot aune mitthi teri talk to
Na pighluga dil eh jwaani teri hot to
Dass fer sher da ni rutba ki reh gya
Je oh vi gya pattya rakaane cat walk to
Oh zindgi nu reejha nal maande aa baithke
Koi chakkr ni meeru bai khada jado back te
Ho asi befikre 9 10 vje sojiye
Ni sathon gallan adhi raat honiya ni chat te
Ni chattya ni kde v yaara ne billo thukk ke
Oh jo vi kita shar-e-aam kreya ni lukk ke
Oh Kayi saale raula pake kehn asi ki aa
Te sara kujh dssya ae mittra di chupp ne
Jo tappde aa salya nu shittra di ghaat ni
Oh fer vekhi baith jaane sara chupp chaap ni
Ohh kehnde ne ke saade naalo vadda koi vaily ni
Te Dhaai saah ne ch*** de utte bhora maas ni
Neet saaf rabb ne vi kujh ni lakoya kude
Tension ni len koi dinda bai saroya kude
Dhannwaad karda va saareya da dil to
Haaye pauna si punjab kattha lentar te hoya kude
Ho dunia ta jitti baitha hun kithe haar da
Jhool jhool ture kude pota jagtar da
Oh jihna hun takk aukh vich hi aa kattli
Ni maapeya nu geda mai lwauna ik bahar da
Ho guru ghar jaake bhala sareyaa da mangda
Ho adhi cho vi adhi cheej doojeya na vand da
Ho mai ni kehnda rabb bahla deyi jawe menu
Jinna mera banda onna hi ohto mangda

snippet.title: 2025 ஆடி கிருத்திகை எந்த நாளில் வருகிறது? வழிபடும் & விரத முறை | Aadi Krithigai fasting & worship
snippet.description:
#ஆடிகிருத்திகை #aadikrithigai #desamangaiyarkarasi #desamangayarkarasi #தேசமங்கையர்க்கரசி 

திருப்புகழ் 1

சந்தம் 
தனதனன தான தத்த தனதனன தான தத்த
தனதனன தான தத்த    தனதான

திருப்புகழ் பாடல் 
சரணகம லால யத்தை அரைநிமிஷ நேர மட்டில்
தவமுறைதி யானம் வைக்க   அறியாத

சடகசட மூட மட்டி பவவினையி லேச னித்த
தமியன்மிடி யால்ம யக்க    முறுவேனோ

கருணைபுரி யாதி ருப்ப தெனகுறையி வேளை செப்பு
கயிலைமலை நாதர் பெற்ற    குமரோனே

கடகபுய மீதி ரத்ந மணியணிபொன் மாலே செச்சை
கமழுமண மார்க டப்ப    மணிவோனே

தருணமிதை யாமி குத்த கனமதுறு நீள்ச வுக்ய
சகலசெல்வ யோக மிக்க    பெருவாழ்வு

தகைமைசிவ ஞான முத்தி பரகதியு நீகொ டுத்து
தவிபுரிய வேணு நெய்த்த    வடிவேலா

அருணதள பாத பத்ம மதுநிதமு மேது திக்க
அரியதமிழ் தான ளித்த    மயில்வீரா

அதிசயம நேக முற்ற பழநிமலை மீது தித்த
அழகதிரு வேர கத்தின்    முருகோனே.

THIRUPUGAZH 1 IN ENGLISH

CHARANA KAMALALA YATHTHAI ARAINIMISHA NERA MATTIL
THAVAMURAI DHIYANAM VAIKKA    ARIYADHA

SADAKASADA MOODA MATTI BHAVA VINAIYILE JANITHTHA
THAMIYAN MIDIYAL MAYAKKAM    URUVENO

KARUNAIPURI YAADHI RUPPA DHENAKURAIYI VELAI SEPPU
KAYILAIMALAI NATHAR PETRA     KUMARONE

KADAKAPUYA MEETHI RATHNA MANIYANIPON MALAE SECHAI
KAMAZHU MANA MAR KADAPPAM    ANIVONE

THARUNAM IDHAIYA MIGUTHTHA KANAMADHURU NEEL SAVUKYA
SAKALASELVA YOGA MIKKA     PERUVAZHVU

THAGAIMAISIVA NYANA MUTHTHI PARAGATHIYU NEE KODUTH
UDHAVIPURIYA VENU NEYTHTHA    VADIVELA

ARUNADHALA PADHA PADHMAM ADHUNIDHAMUME THUDHIKKA
ARIYATHAMIZH THAN ALITHTHA    MAYILVEERA

ADHISAYAM ANEGAM UTRA PAZHANIMALAI MEEDH UDHITHTHA
AZHAGATHIRU VERAGATHTHIN    MURUGONE.

திருப்புகழ் 2

சந்தம் 
தனதான தத்த தனதான தத்த
தனதான தத்த  தனதான

திருப்புகழ் பாடல் 

செகமாயை யுற்றெ னகவாழ்வில் வைத்த
திருமாது கெர்ப்ப     முடலூறித்

தெசமாத முற்றி வடிவாய்நி லத்தில்
திரமாய ளித்த      பொருளாகி

மகவாவி னுச்சி விழியாந நத்தில்
மலைநேர்பு யத்தி     லுறவாடி

மடிமீத டுத்து விளையாடி நித்த
மணிவாயின் முத்தி     தரவேணும்

முகமாய மிட்ட குறமாதி னுக்கு
முலைமேல ணைக்க     வருநீதா

முதுமாம றைக்கு ளொருமாபொ ருட்குள்
மொழியேயு ரைத்த     குருநாதா

தகையாதெ னக்கு னடிகாண வைத்த
தனியேர கத்தின்     முருகோனே

தருகாவி ரிக்கு வடபாரி சத்தில்
சமர்வேலெ டுத்த     பெருமாளே.

THIRUPPUGHAZH 2 IN ENGLISH 

SEGA MAYAI UTREN AGA VAZHVIL VAITHTHA
THIRUMADHU GERBAM     UDAL URI

DHESA MADHA MUTRI VADIVAY NILATHTHIL
THIRAMAY ALITHTHA      PORULAGI

MAGAVAVIN UCHCHI VIZHI ANANATHTHIL
MALAI NER BUYATHTHIL     URAVADI

MADIMEE DHADUTHTHU VILAIYADI NITHTHAM
MANIVAYIN MUTHTHI      THARAVENUM

MUGA MAYAM ITTA KURA MADHINUKKU
MULAIMEL ANAIKKA  VARU    NEEDHA

MUDHU MA MARAIKKUL ORU MA PORUTKUL
MOZHIYE URAITHTHA      GURUNATHA

THAGAIYADH ENAKKUN ADI KANA VAITHTHA
THANI ERAGATHTHIN      MURUGONE

THARU KAVIRIKKU VADA PARISATHTHIL
SAMAR VEL EDUTHTHA     PERUMALE.

ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

***About Our Channel***

Van life is very common in western countries. So in this channel at E Bull Jet, we are featuring van life in India. This channel will showcase the real-life in India and nearby countries.

We are Abin and Libin, siblings belonging to Irutty, a locality in Kannur District of Kerala, India. We aim to explore India and nearby countries in a van that's converted into a home. In this journey, we will sleep, cook, and travel in our van and will ex cover places at minimal expenses.  

We would like to bring our Van life though this channel - E BULL JET

പാശ്ചാത്യ രാജ്യങ്ങളിൽ ഉള്ള പോലെ നമ്മുടെ രാജ്യത്തും ഒരു വാൻ ലൈഫ് നടത്തുകയും അതിന്റെ മാസ്മരിക കാഴ്ചകൾ പ്രിയപെട്ടവരിലേക്ക് എത്തിക്കുകയും ആണ് 'ഈ ബുൾ ജെറ്റ്' എന്ന ഈ കൊച്ചു ചാനൽ കൊണ്ട് ഞങ്ങൾ ഉദ്ദേശിക്കുന്നത്.

കണ്ണൂർ ജില്ലയിലെ ഇരുട്ടി എന്ന പ്രദേശത്തു ജീവിക്കുന്ന സഹോദരങ്ങളാണ് ഞങ്ങൾ, പേര് എബിൻ, ലിബിൻ. നമ്മുടെ രാജ്യവും, അയാൾ രാജ്യങ്ങളും കുറഞ്ഞ ചിലവിൽ കാണുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം. അതിനായി ഒരു മിനി വാൻ ഞങ്ങൾ വീടാക്കി മാറ്റി അതിൽ യാത്ര ചെയുന്നു, വഴിയിൽ പാചകം ചെയ്തു കുറഞ്ഞു ചിലവിൽ ലോകം കാണുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം. 

ഞങ്ങൾ കാണുന്നതും കേള്കുന്നതുമായ കാര്യങ്ങൾ ഈ ചാനലിൽ കൂടെ പങ്കുവെക്കുക എന്നതാണ് ലക്ഷ്യം.

PLEASE SUBSCRIBE TO THIS CHANNEL AND ENABLE NOTIFICATIONS: 
"Van Life Is our Passion"
"Your dream our world
This is our vision and mission - E BULL JET

Dream with Us. Thank You. :)

snippet.title: प्रेमिका बनना आसान है पर बीवी बनाना उतना ही मुश्किल है - Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen - Biwi No.1
snippet.description:
► Click here to Subscribe the channel : https://bit.ly/3HS054l 

प्रेमिका बनना आसान है पर बीवी बनाना उतना ही मुश्किल है - Salman Khan, Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen ज़बरदस्त सीन - Biwi No.1 - Hindi ज़बरदस्त सीन

Get ready for a rollercoaster of emotions with Biwi No.1 (1999), a delightful comedy directed by David Dhawan. This film features an ensemble cast including Salman Khan, Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen, Anil Kapoor, and Tabu, delivering a perfect blend of humor and drama.

The story revolves around Prem (Salman Khan), a wealthy man leading a blissful life with his wife Pooja (Karisma Kapoor) and their two children. Their idyllic existence is disrupted when Prem becomes infatuated with Rupali (Sushmita Sen), a glamorous model. As Prem's extramarital affair unfolds, Pooja discovers the betrayal and, with the help of her supportive family and friends, devises a plan to win back her husband and restore her family's happiness. The narrative explores themes of love, trust, and the importance of family bonds, all wrapped in a comedic package. 

Biwi No.1 was both a critical and commercial success, becoming the second highest-grossing Hindi film of 1999. The film received several accolades, with Sushmita Sen winning the Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actress for her portrayal of Rupali. The movie's soundtrack, composed by Anu Malik, also contributed to its widespread popularity. 

Experience the laughter, tears, and ultimate redemption in Biwi No.1 (1999)!

◾ Film :  Biwi No.1 (1999)
◾ Director: David Dhawan
◾ Writers: Kamal Haasan, Rumi Jaffery, Ikram Akhtar
◾ Producers: Vashu Bhagnani
◾ Cast: Salman Khan, Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen, Anil Kapoor, Tabu
◾ Music: Anu Malik
◾ Genre: Comedy, Drama
◾ Language: Hindi
